sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>Browser/Mobile
    participant Kong as Kong Gateway<br/>API Router
    participant Keycloak as Keycloak<br/>Auth
    participant Service as Service<br/>Node.js
    participant Cache as Redis<br/>Cache
    participant Prisma as Prisma ORM<br/>Query Builder
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>Database
    participant NATS as NATS JetStream<br/>Events

    Note over Client,NATS: Request Flow

    Client->>Kong: 1. POST /api/invoices<br/>(with JWT token)
    Kong->>Keycloak: 2. Validate JWT<br/>Check Scopes
    Keycloak-->>Kong: 3. Token Valid ✓
    Kong->>Service: 4. Route Request<br/>/invoices Handler

    Note over Service,Cache: Service Processing

    Service->>Cache: 5. Check Cache<br/>get:invoices:list
    Cache-->>Service: 6. Cache Miss
    Service->>Prisma: 7. Query Invoice.findMany()<br/>with filters, relations
    Prisma->>PG: 8. SELECT invoices...<br/>with JOINs to line items

    Note over PG: Database Query

    PG->>PG: 9. ACID Transaction<br/>Execute Query
    PG-->>Prisma: 10. Return typed rows<br/>Invoice[]

    Note over Prisma,Service: Response Building

    Prisma-->>Service: 11. Typed Response<br/>Invoice[] (type-safe)
    Service->>Cache: 12. Store in Cache<br/>set:invoices:list TTL=5m
    Service->>NATS: 13. Publish Event<br/>invoice.listed

    Note over NATS: Event Streaming

    NATS->>NATS: 14. Store Event<br/>JetStream Persistence
    NATS-->>Service: 15. Event ACK

    Note over Service,Client: Response

    Service-->>Kong: 16. JSON Response<br/>200 OK
    Kong-->>Client: 17. Return Response<br/>with headers

    Note over Client: Client Receives<br/>Type-safe data

    rect rgba(100, 200, 100, 0.2)
        Note over Service,NATS: Event-Driven Subscribers
        NATS->>Service: 18. Durable Consumer<br/>Receives invoice.listed<br/>Updates Analytics
        NATS->>Service: 19. Another Consumer<br/>Receives invoice.listed<br/>Triggers Notification
    end
